Kim-ku3: Sou2-i2 goa2 ka-ki7 iam3-ounn3, ti7 tin5-ai kap he2-hu e5 tiong-kan hoan2-hoe2. (Ioh-pek-ki3 42: 6)
Tann sio2 peng5-iu2 u7 chit8 e5 A-peh-a3 kio3 cho3 A-hian3 i si7 khia7-khi2 ti7 soann-lai7, khi2-thau5 i si7 teh chho3-chha5, hit-liap8 soann e5 chu2-lang5 si7 cheng3-hu2, sou2-i2 i u7 khi3 chhoe7 cheng3-hu2 ka7 i kong2 hit liap8 soann lai5 soe3--goa2; tui3 cheng3-hu2 chou chin siok8, ti7 hia keng-eng5 tui3 soann than3 chin choe7 chinn5, au7-lai5 chiu7 chhoa7 bou2 ia7 sinn-kiann2. A-hian3 i tui3 se3-han3 to7 u7 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8, m7-ku2 jip8-khi3 ti7 soann-lai7 long2 bo5 le2-pai3-tng5, chong2-si7 i ti7 chhiu7-na5-lai7 chhoa7 i kiann2-ji5 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, ia7 in2-chhoa7 hiah e5 ti7 hia hou7 i chhiann3 e5 lang5 lai5 le2-pai3, u7 e5 lai5 u7 e5 tian-to3 thi2-chhio3 i, ka7 i kong2, ¡§Chit-chun7 lin2 e5 Siong7-te3 hou7 li2 khui-tioh8 soann than3 toa7-chinn5, li2 chiah teh pai3 Siong7-te3, na7 siat-su2 Siong7-te3 hou7 li2 e5 ke-hoe2 sit-pai7 bo5 chinn5, goa2 khoann3 li2 long2 boe7 ki3-tit u7 Siong7-te3.¡¨
A-hian3 hiann ka7 i kong2, Goa2 chhut-si3 e5 si5 Siong7-te3 ia7-si7 hou7 goa2 khia7 ti7 chin san3-hiong e5 ka-teng5, tak8-jit8 toe3 lau7-pe7 si3-koe3 khi3 khioh-chha5, siong5-siong5 bo5 chinn5 thang eng7, u7 si5 phoa3-pinn7 ia7 bo5 ioh8-a2 thang chiah8, chi2-u7 goa2 e5 pa-pa thoe3 goa2 ki5-to2 lim chui2 cho3 ioh8-a2; goa2 hiah-nih8 teh kan-khou2 goa2 to teh keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3, na7 siat-su2 chit-chun7 Siong7-te3 hou7 goa2 khah san3-hiong tu2-tioh8 loa7-nih8 toa7 e5 chai-e7, goa2 ia7-si7 beh keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3. A-hian3 hiann e5 su7-giap8 ju2-cho3 ju2-toa7, kiann2-sun ia7 chin heng-ong7.
Keng-koe3 3 ni5 au7, i e5 toa7-kiann2 kap hiah e5 sun-a2 u7 chit8-jit8, ti7 soann-nih8 e5 chhu3-a2 teh hioh tiong-tau3, m7-chai sim2-mih8 goan5-in hut-jian5 hoe2 sio soann, A-hian3 e5 kiann2 mia5 kio3 Se-hiong5, chiu7 kin2 khi2-lai5 beh phah-hoe2, 3 e5 gin2-na2, 2 e5 ta-pou, 1 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 kap i ti7 chhu3-a2 e5 lai7-bin7 teh khun3, hoe2 teh sio chin kin2 kui e5 liau5-a2 long2 pau khi2-lai5, gin2-na2 cheng-sin5 beh chau2 i2-keng chau2 boe7 chhut-lai5, toa7-siann hoah-hiam3, Se-hiong5 thiann tioh8 i e5 3 e5 kiann2 koann2-kin2 lai5, chau2 jip8-khi3 beh chhoa7 i e5 gin2-na2, chiu7 chong5 jip8 hoe2-tiong pho7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 chhut-lai5, chit8-e7 khoann3 si7 i2-keng sio si2-khi3, lau7-pe7 kui seng-khu hou7 hoe2 sio kau3 chin thiam2, A-hian3 hiann khoann3-tioh8 hoe2 teh sio-soann, ia7-si7 kin2 piann3 khi2-khi3, hoe2 chin iam7 iu5-goan5 si7 hou7 hoe2 sio kah kui seng-khu.
Chit8-e7 kau3-ui7 khoann3-tioh8 kiann2 teh beh si2, 3 e5 sun-a2 long2 hou7 hoe2 sio si2, A-hian3 hiann khoann3 chit8-e7 chin kan-khou2, koh kui seng-khu hou7 hoe2 sio kau3 chit8-pha7, chin thang3-thiann3 thong3-khou2 kui7 ti7 hoe2 sio-lou7 e5 tiong-kan ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 kong2, Siong7-te3 ah, goa2 khoann3 goa2 e5 sin-the2 si7 kek8 bo5 lou7-eng7, la5-sam5, goa2 chhim-chhim thong3-hoe2 jin7-choe7, kiu5 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 i e5 choe7, ki5-to2 liau2 ka7 chiu-ui5 e5 lang5 kong2, Siong7-te3 hou7 goa2 ho2-giah8, hou7 goa2 kiann2-sun, goa2 tioh8 kam2-sia7, chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 ka7 goa2 tho2 tng2-khi3, goa2 ia7 chin kam2-sia7. Chiau3 ku7 jiat8-sim hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, hiah e5 peng5-iu2 khoann3-kinn3 i chiau3-ku7 keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3, tui3 an2-ni chin toa7 siu7 kam2-tong7, chiu7 kap i sann-kap lai5 pai3 Siong7-te3.
Siong7-te3 khoann3-kinn3 A-hian3 an2-ni, chiu7 chiau3 i2-cheng5 koh hou7 i e5 chai5-san2 hok8-goan5, soe3-han3 kiann2 ia7-si7 chin choe7 sun.
